author: Erica Orden
description: Former U.S. Rep. Anthony Weiner, whose sexting scandals ended his political career, pleaded guilty in federal court Friday to exchanging sexually explicit messages with a minor.
title: Anthony Weiner Pleads Guilty Following Sexting Probe

author: Brendan Pierson
description: Former U.S. Congressman Anthony Weiner wept on Friday as he pleaded guilty to sending sexually explicit messages to a teenage girl, capping a "sexting" scandal that played a role in last year's U.S. presidential election during its waning days.
title: Ex-U.S. Congressman Weiner pleads guilty in teen 'sexting' case
